column16: J.  B.   Shuck flies out to center fielder Juan Lagares.
John McDonald doubles (1) on a line drive to left fielder Eric Young.
Hank Conger grounds out, third baseman Josh Satin to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Ian Stewart homers (1) on a fly ball to left center field.   Howie Kendrick scores.
Kole Calhoun triples (1) on a line drive to left fielder Eric Young.
Mike Trout lines out to first baseman Ike Davis.
J.  B.   Shuck grounds out, second baseman Daniel Murphy to first baseman Ike Davis.
Kole Calhoun pops out to shortstop Omar Quintanilla.
Chris Iannetta grounds out, second baseman Daniel Murphy to first baseman Ike Davis.
Raul Ibanez grounds out, third baseman David Wright to first baseman Ike Davis.
Erick Aybar grounds out softly, pitcher John Lannan to first baseman Ike Davis.
Freddie Freeman singles on a line drive to center fielder Juan Lagares.
Jay Bruce homers (2) on a line drive to right center field.    Brandon Phillips scores.
Joey Votto grounds out, third baseman David Wright to first baseman Lucas Duda.   Brandon Phillips to 2nd.
Brandon Phillips singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Eric Young.
Nationals challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was upheld: Danny Espinosa grounds out softly, third baseman David Wright to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Anthony Rendon homers (1) on a fly ball to left field.   Jose Lobaton scores.    Adam LaRoche scores.
